snippet.title: My Big Sister - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Meet Luzia, a sarcastic twelve-year-old with a playful sense of humor. If you believe what she says, My Big Sister is an RPG-like adventure game that is not about her but about her sister Sombria. My Big Sister will release on May 8th

http://www.ratalaikagames.com/games/mybigsister.php
